00042   if (dfsch_list_length_check(args)!=(count)) \

00112     dfsch_error("exception:not-a-type", super);
00113   }

00116                                        (dfsch_type_t*)super));

00195 DFSCH_DEFINE_FORM_IMPL(define, "Define variable or procedure"){
00196 
00197   MIN_ARGS(args,1);  
00198 
00199   object_t* name = dfsch_car(args);
00200 
00201   if (DFSCH_PAIR_P(name)){
00202     object_t* lambda = dfsch_named_lambda(env,dfsch_cdr(name),
00203                                           dfsch_cdr(args),
00204                                           dfsch_car(name));
00205     name = DFSCH_FAST_CAR(name);
00206     return dfsch_define(name, lambda ,env);
00207   }else{
00208     object_t* value = dfsch_eval(dfsch_car(dfsch_cdr(args)),env);
00209     return dfsch_define(name,value,env);
00210   }
00211 }

00214                        "Define variable only if it is not already defined"){

00217 
00218   DFSCH_OBJECT_ARG(args, name);
00219   DFSCH_OBJECT_ARG_OPT(args, value, NULL);
00220   DFSCH_ARG_END(args);

00223     value = dfsch_eval(value, env);

00228   }

00456 DFSCH_DEFINE_PRIMITIVE(for_each, 0){
00457   object_t* func;
00458   object_t* list;
00459   size_t len;
00460   size_t i;
00461 
00462   DFSCH_OBJECT_ARG(args, func);
00463   list = dfsch_zip(args);
00464 
00465   if (!list){
00466     return NULL;
00467   }
00468 
00469   while (dfsch_pair_p(list)){
00470     dfsch_apply(func, dfsch_car(list));
00471     list = dfsch_cdr(list);
00472   }
00473   
00474   return NULL;
00475 }
00476 DFSCH_DEFINE_PRIMITIVE(map, 0){
00477   object_t* func;
00478   object_t* list;
00479   object_t* head = NULL;
00480   object_t* tail;
00481 
00482   DFSCH_OBJECT_ARG(args, func);
00483   list = dfsch_zip(args);
00484 
00485   if (!list){
00486     return NULL;
00487   }
00488 
00489   while (dfsch_pair_p(list)){
00490     object_t *t = dfsch_cons(dfsch_apply(func, dfsch_car(list)), NULL);
00491     if (!head){
00492       head = tail = t;
00493     }else{
00494       dfsch_set_cdr(tail, t);
00495       tail = t;
00496     }
00497     list = dfsch_cdr(list);
00498   }
00499   
00500   return head;
00501 }
00502 DFSCH_DEFINE_PRIMITIVE(filter, 0){
00503   object_t* func;
00504   object_t* list;
00505   object_t* head = NULL;
00506   object_t* tail;
00507 
00508   DFSCH_OBJECT_ARG(args, func);
00509   DFSCH_OBJECT_ARG(args, list);
00510   DFSCH_ARG_END(args);
00511 
00512   while (dfsch_pair_p(list)){
00513     object_t* item =  dfsch_car(list);
00514     object_t* t;
00515 
00516     if (dfsch_apply(func, 
00517                     dfsch_list(1, item))){
00518       t = dfsch_cons(item, NULL);
00519 
00520       if (!head){
00521         head = tail = t;
00522       }else{
00523         dfsch_set_cdr(tail, t);
00524         tail = t;
00525       }
00526     }
00527     list = dfsch_cdr(list);
00528   }
00529   
00530   return head;
00531 }
00532 DFSCH_DEFINE_PRIMITIVE(reduce, 0){
00533   object_t* func;
00534   object_t* list;
00535   object_t* tally;
00536 
00537   DFSCH_OBJECT_ARG(args, func);
00538   DFSCH_OBJECT_ARG(args, list);
00539   DFSCH_ARG_END(args);
00540 
00541   if (!dfsch_pair_p(list)){
00542     return NULL;
00543   }
00544 
00545   tally = dfsch_car(list);
00546   list = dfsch_cdr(list);
00547 
00548   while (dfsch_pair_p(list)) {
00549     tally = dfsch_apply(func, dfsch_list(2, tally, dfsch_car(list)));
00550     list = dfsch_cdr(list);
00551   }
00552   
00553   return tally;
00554 }
